  • Field Details

    • pluginName

      protected final String pluginName
      Gets the name of the plugin that owns this StructureType.

    • simpleName

      protected final String simpleName
      Gets the simple name of this StructureType. Note that this is always in lower case!

      The simple name is the name of the StructureType without the plugin name. For example, "windmill", "bigdoor", "flag", etc.

    • version

      protected final int version
      Gets the version of this StructureType. Note that changing the version creates a whole new StructureType and you'll have to take care of the transition.

    • localizationKey

      protected final String localizationKey
      Obtains the value of this type that represents the key in the translation system.

      protected StructureType(String pluginName, String simpleName, int version, List<MovementDirection> validOpenDirections, String localizationKey)
      Constructs a new StructureType. Don't forget to also register it using StructureTypeManager.register(StructureType).
      Parameters:
      pluginName - The name of the plugin that owns this StructureType.
      simpleName - The 'simple' name of this StructureType. E.g. "Flag", or "Windmill".
      version - The version of this StructureType.

    • getValidOpenDirections

      public Set<MovementDirection> getValidOpenDirections()
      Gets a set of all theoretically valid MovementDirection for this given type. It does NOT take the physical aspects of the AbstractStructure into consideration. Therefore, the actual set of valid MovementDirections is most likely going to be a subset of those returned by this method.
      Returns:
      A set of all valid MovementDirection for this given type.

      Returns:
      A list of all valid MovementDirection for this given type.
